          <h2>What is Plantah?</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1">
            <p>Plantah is a garden planning web tool. It is an amalgamation of
              all of the gardening information that I've wanted easy access to.
              It was designed out of the desire to make it simpler to create a
              garden plan, by placing all of the
              information that you need, in an easy-to-find format. For you, I hope
              that Plantah becomes a resource that you can rely on to either begin
              your gardening experience, or widen your experience by giving you fresh ideas
              for new combinations in your beds.
            </p>
