        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1">
            <p>Plantah will be a robust web application, where users can design and share
            their own, unique garden plans. The tool has been built to be extendable
            to accomodate many users, although those features are not currently active.
            Those users will be able to model their plans with a feature that allows them
            to diagram their garden beds. Using Plantah's
            database, they will have immediate access to how many of those plants they
            can fit into a given area, and whether that plant's neighbors are 'friends'
            or 'foes.'</p>
